{"title":"OrNot’s New UV Hooded Trail Shirt Offers Sun Protection & Chill On/Off the Bike Vibes","link":"https://bikerumor.com/ornot-uv-hooded-trail-shirt/","date":1746195625000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-hero.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" alt=\"(Photos / OrNot)\" /></p>\n<p>I think we can all appreciate a nice, comfy shirt. Well, what if you could get one that had a hood and provided actual protection from the sun, but was still quick drying and lightweight? What if I told you that this shirt was made in the USA using Italian-made, Oeko-Tex-approved recycled fabric? Sounds like a dream, right? Well, dream no more, OrNot has a new <a href=\"https://www.ornotbike.com/collections/mens_shirts_and_pullovers/products/mens-uv-hooded-trail-shirt-olive\" target=\"_blank\">men’s</a> and <a href=\"https://www.ornotbike.com/collections/womens-shirts-and-pullovers/products/womens-hooded-uv-trail-shirt-stone-blue\" target=\"_blank\">women’s</a> UV Hooded Trail Shirt that is all of these things, and you get all of it for a pretty affordable price. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-woods.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-woods.webp\" alt=\"OrNot UV Hooded Trail Shirt in the woods\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-woods.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-woods-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-woods-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-woods-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-woods-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-woods-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / OrNot)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s sewn in California, and uses the Oeko-Tex-approved recycled fabric. So, that means you can wear it knowing that you are seamlessly blending performance with being environmentally responsible. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-trees.webp\"><img width=\"854\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-trees.webp\" alt=\"OrNot UV Hooded Trail Shirt in the trees\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-trees.webp 854w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-trees-200x300.webp 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-trees-80x120.webp 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-in-the-trees-768x1151.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-girl-sitting.webp\"><img width=\"854\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-girl-sitting.webp\" alt=\"OrNot UV Hooded Trail Shirt girl sitting\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-girl-sitting.webp 854w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-girl-sitting-200x300.webp 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-girl-sitting-80x120.webp 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-girl-sitting-768x1151.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new UV Hooded Shirt sports bike-specific tailoring with a loose fit, which allows for air flow. With the UPF 30 sun protection, the bike-specific fit, and quick-drying breathability, this shirt is the perfect choice to keep you cool and comfortable from sunrise to sunset.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-outta-the-saddle.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"854\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-outta-the-saddle.webp\" alt=\"OrNot UV Hooded Trail Shirt outta the saddle\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-outta-the-saddle.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-outta-the-saddle-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-outta-the-saddle-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-outta-the-saddle-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-outta-the-saddle-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-outta-the-saddle-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Along with the bike-specific tailoring, there’s also a convenient rear pocket. Perfect for a snack, sunglasses, or other small goodies and essentials. The really cool thing about the handy-dandy pocket is that inside you’ll find a hidden <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ornot-x-chris-mcnally-limited-ultra-light-boxers/\" target=\"_blank\">Chris McNally sketchbook print</a>.  </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-lable.webp\"><img width=\"854\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-lable.webp\" alt=\"OrNot UV Hooded Trail Shirt lable\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/OrNot-UV-Hooded-Trail-Shirt-